        <item>
            <title>0.8.1</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 17:43:05 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>801</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.8.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Jarvis 0.8.1</h2>
<p><b>Telegram stability fix.</b> Fixes a crash that could hit when disconnecting
or reconnecting Telegram, or quitting Jarvis while Telegram was connected. The
earlier safeguard from 0.7.2 could be raced by a quick shutdown; Jarvis now
stands clear of the Telegram engine's teardown in every order of events, and
this exact sequence is covered by tests so it stays fixed.</p>
<p>All of the 0.8.0 redesign — the app library, the Meetings control, and your
day in the Hub — is unchanged.</p>
]]></description>
